main event: A strange white object was seen hovering overhead in Dublin, Georgia on November 3, 1957.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 90 minutes.,The object's movement was described as slow and irregular.,No photographs were taken during the sighting.,The report indicated that the necessary information for proper evaluation was missing.,The observer was identified as a 55-year-old Civil Defense Administrator.
witness description: 55 years old, Civil Defense Administrator in Dublin, Georgia
